# =============================================================================
# WORKFLOW INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================

# Team Workflow:
# 1. All team members (@cdmagni, @cuajov6, @maurotbf, @simperiale) can:
#    - Create feature branches
#    - Make changes to tareas_back/
#    - Create merge requests
#    - Review each other's code
#
# 2. Only @cuajov6 can:
#    - Approve and merge to main branch
#    - Modify security-sensitive files
#    - Override protected branch rules
#
# 3. Protected Branch Setup:
#    - Branch: main
#    - Allowed to merge: @cuajov6
#    - Allowed to push: @cuajov6
#    - Require approval from code owners: Yes
#    - Minimum number of approvals: 1 (from @cuajov6)
#
# 4. Merge Request Process:
#    - Any team member creates MR
#    - Other team members can review and comment
#    - @cuajov6 must approve and merge
#    - Code owner approval is required for main branch 